African Marine Solutions Group (Amsol) &#8211; a consortium comprising deal makers at RMB Ventures, Pan-African Capital Holdings, Mineworkers Capital Partners and Smit Amandla Marine employees &#8211; recently acquired Smit Amandla Marine from a Dutch maritime group.In this video, Andrew Aitken and Mbongeni Madonsela, dealmakers at RMB, share the rationale behind the deal.They answer the following questions: This video was produced by Moneyweb and sponsored by RMB.